article.description: — Jackson Stormo had 20 points as Siena edged past Niagara 60-56 on Friday night.
article.headline: Stormo scores 20 to lead Siena past Niagara 60-56
article.linkText: Stormo scores 20 to lead Siena past Niagara 60-56
article.story: ALBANY, N.Y. -- — Jackson Stormo had 20 points as Siena edged past Niagara 60-56 on Friday night. Colby Rogers had 11 points for Siena (7-8, 4-3 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Jared Billups added eight rebounds. Anthony Gaines had six rebounds. Sam Iorio had 15 points and 10 rebounds for the Purple Eagles (8-11, 3-7). Noah Thomasson added 15 points and six rebounds. Jordan Cintron had 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
